	(text_box "NOTE: The ZID uses a FFC/FPC cable to connect to the POD. The Z80 signals are 1:1 on the ZID. Since the FFC cable is single side, it means the signal to pin on the POD connector are 1:40/40:1.\nThe Z80 Socket/Pins are 1:1. So, Pin-1 on the POD connector goes to Pin-40 on the Z80 Socket."
